title: Board of Governors Monetary Base, Adjusted for Changes in Reserve Requirements (DISCONTINUED)
notes: This series has been discontinued. As of July 11, 2013 data in the new H.3 statistical release are no longer adjusted for regulatory changes in reserve requirements and are no longer seasonally adjusted. The Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis publishes adjusted monetary base at https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/AMBSL.
